{"tid":601610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女子鑽石山火葬場墮斃","createTime":"2018-03-22T10:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T15:17:19.000Z","uid":41404,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"50024a64ce5ec015223ac875d59f328d5b917ff3","tid":601610,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T10:46:46.000Z","msg":"黃大仙鑽石山火葬場，下午1時許，一名女子被發現由火葬場內的思親堂骨灰龕大廈高處墮下，重傷倒地，救護員接報到場證實她當場死亡，警方正展開調查。警員隨後在8樓發現一對鞋及一個斜孭袋，死者姓張54歲，但未撿獲遺書，初步相信她爬過8樓1米高石牆墮樓。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180322/57980230\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180322%2F57980230&d=G4MbdYmg0nSFIzY5CecUOxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=a7348039\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180322%2F57980230&h=f90c9a7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180322/57980230</a>"},{"pid":"89f24c0cc8875c59c7ce4e121ae6a76469287c40","tid":601610,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T10:47:43.000Z","msg":"鑽石山女子墮樓亡，中午12時53分，鑽石山靈灰安置所有市民報案，指聽到「嘭」一聲巨響後，發現一名女子倒臥於思親堂地上重傷昏迷，懷疑她從高處墮下。救護員接報趕至，證實該名姓張（54歲）女子已當場死亡。警方用帳篷遮蓋屍體，在現場檢獲一對鞋及一個手袋調查，但未有檢獲遺書。 <br />\n<br />\n由於警方在8樓圍欄旁發現一張椅子，經初步調查後，懷疑死者以椅子踏腳一躍而下，相信事件無可疑，死者死因有待驗屍後確定。現場消息指，死者家住屯門，有情緒病紀錄，今晨離開寓所前向家人指前往購物，豈料在鑽石山出事，警方正調查其尋死原因。 <br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線： <br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222 <br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000 <br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288 <br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255 <br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000 <br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281 <br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180322/mobile/bkn-20180322130212934-0322_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180322%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180322130212934-0322_00822_001.html&d=G4MbdYmg0nSFIzY5CecUOxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=07f3abe7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180322/mobile/bkn-20180322130212934-0322_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0cdda105475544abf3b393ae4787063beab9a1b9","tid":601610,"uid":33439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T10:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f80454f309545fddb6e179b790841fab1c5cdc","tid":601610,"uid":10451,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T10:52:11.000Z","msg":"搵替身咁簡單"},{"pid":"26ac0f3d5157fe42800ccee0cf8ee5cffef9317f","tid":601610,"uid":38352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T10:52:42.000Z","msg":"殯儀館都唔駛去"},{"pid":"8eec4e0de45a731d8bcfd8f6b371d6261f4e47bf","tid":601610,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T10:56:05.000Z","msg":"黃大仙鑽石山火葬場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能有親人走咗好唔捨得順手死埋"},{"pid":"e994cbc4dcc93374dedccd22df024fb1d6d65012","tid":601610,"uid":52006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T12:02:03.000Z","msg":"搵替身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c90b881c173439fbf13247a0fd137d8985d8bc","tid":601610,"uid":5739,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T12:38:20.000Z","msg":"鑽石山女子墮樓亡，中午12時53分，鑽石山靈灰安置<span style=\"color: red;\">所有市民報案</span>，指聽到「嘭」一聲巨響後<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji